data.description: In-town Grand Rapids home featuring fresh updates to: paint, flooring, tiled tub, bathroom flooring, and counter top.  Main level master bedroom featuring large soaking tub and ample closet space!  Spacious kitchen/dining area is perfect for hosting your family gatherings. Huge upstairs bedroom includes a 1/2 bath and sitting area. Lower level features tongue and groove, new carpet, washer/dryer, and two additional 9 x 12 bonus bedrooms (non-egress) making this home potentially 5 bedrooms. Two stall detached garage for the cold winter months. A must see home which is conveniently located near schools and downtown shopping.
